Powersweeper
============
A bot designed for solving Minesweeper games.

Compiling
=========
This project is managed by Apache [maven][1] which takes care of all dependencies and build
steps.

To compile the application you will need to install [maven][1] and execute `mvn clean package` within the project
directory. This will automatically download all dependencies and compile the project into an executable jar which will
be available within the `target/` directory.

Contributing
============
Everybody is free to contribute to this project. Please check out the code guidelines within the `contrib/` folder for
more information on the requirements.

